Job Description
This role is responsible for Branch related business and MIS analysis. The role holder is also responsible for preparing Statistics for Economic Departments and handling UAT for Fincon related projects
Support in Oracle / Automation Projects (UAT for OFSAA/DW/BI)
Prepare and analyze Customer Account Activity Report
Consistently initiate DAO/ Data Cleansing
Proactively prepare and submit Economic Departments/ Branch Statistics
Daily submission of Islamic Inter Co Reconciliation and Singapore - HO Due to / Due from Reconciliation
Analyze Loans / Deposits by Branch / Emirate
Review of Br GL and Br P&L variances
Ensure total of all Br GL’s and Br P&L’s tie up to the CONGL and CONPL
Prepare & submit the APR/Revenue/Expense based MI-Reports by Branch
Assist in any other Ad-hoc MIS & Reports as and when required.
Desired Profile
Bachelor's Degree
At least 5 to 7 years of relevant work experience
Key Skills
Good Communication Skills
Computer Literate
